org.grouplens.lenskit.vectors

Class ImmutableSparseVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.lenskit.vectors.SparseVector
      • org.grouplens.lenskit.vectors.ImmutableSparseVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<VectorEntry>

    @Immutable
public final class ImmutableSparseVector
extends SparseVector
implements java.io.Serializable
    Immutable sparse vectors. These vectors cannot be changed, even by other code, and are therefore safe to store and are thread-safe.

    Use create(java.util.Map), SparseVector.empty(), immutable(), or MutableSparseVector.freeze() to create immutable sparse vectors.
